# It seems that I encountered an error while trying to insert iron ore into the furnace. The error message indicates that I have no iron ore left in my inventory.

# Let's review my current inventory:
# - 2 transport belts
# - 2 stone bricks
# - 8 stones
# - 5 copper ore
# - 1 copper plate
# - 4 copper cables
# - 1 iron gear wheel

# I do not have any iron ore available, which means I need to gather some before I can proceed to smelt iron plates.

# I will move to the nearest iron ore resource to gather the necessary iron ore for smelting.

move_to(nearest(Resource.IronOre))  # Move towards the nearest iron ore resource location to gather iron ore.
